      "amazon_header": "(unrecognized columns fall back here)",
      "type": "json",
      "note": "Documented opt-outs (2026-07-11): 'Estado del producto' and 'Producto para vender' remain on ~216 historical UK Spanish-locale rows — item_condition is a unique-key member (never backfilled in place); the parser maps both for all future ingests."
